<paragraph id="1DE935E14182BAC8EF384F1290478102" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Dry scrub and deserts, principally in the United States Southwest and Mexico but of unknown status in Guatemala and apparently naturalised in Venezuela. It is found from low altitudes up to at least 2300 m.</paragraph>
